Class Role

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.realtime.storage.security.Role
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPolicy

    public class Role
extends Object
implements IPolicy
    Defines a role which is a set of rules that control access to the Storage database.

    RTCS Development team
